HEADWORD: Xanthoxylene
<hw>Xan*thox"y*lene</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Xanthoxylum</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A liquid
hydrocarbon of the terpene series extracted from the seeds of a Japanese
prickly ash (<spn>Xanthoxylum pipertium</spn>) as an aromatic
oil.</def>⟦br⟧
